    "This search generated 344 documents written in English and published between January 2015 and July 2022.",
    "However, we limited our search to articles published or in the press by excluding book chapters, conference papers, editorials, errata, data papers, and review papers, and we got 240 articles.",
    "Finally, by further scrutinizing the articles for irrelevant terms such as high-frequency band, closing hours, peak hours, work hours, intraday snapshots, etc., we obtained a final list of 189 articles as a literature sample from 2015 to 2022.",
    "This bibliometric dataset was analyzed using a bibliometric technique.",
    "The year-wise publication trends are shown in Fig. 1."
